@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(0.21)
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.80) * wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.53)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(0.22))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.26 + v2 + 0.72) - (v2 + 0.90 / v0 + 0.01)) / (v0 + 0.25))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.37) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.21)) + wp.exp((v2 + 0.68 - tmp + 0.85)))
    v0 = v0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.75)
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
